replies.body:
I think they're shifting Crit away from Assassins. You don't want to bank your entire Assassination attempt to 35% RNG, do you? ADCs can afford it because they also get crit from Shiv, PD, or Rapidfire. Assassins don't.

Armor Penetration is their intended Assassin stat, from the looks of it. It's on Youmuu's still, and they added it onto Maw of Malmortius. With both of those, you'll basically deal true damage to anything without Armor.

